grep
-----
for searching particular word we use grep command

ex grep root /etc/passwd

it gives you only statements containing the word root

LESS/MORE/HEAD/TAIL
--------------------
ex cat /etc/passwd

gives the data

less /etc/passwd

gives you less data

more /etc/passwd

gives you more data

head /etc/passwd

gives you top 10 lines data

head -3 /etc/passwd

gives you top 3 lines

tail -3 /etc/passwd

gives you bottom 3 lines

sort
-----

sort filename

gives you the file content in alphabetical order
`



